<P><BR><BR>Namate friends,<BR><BR>Note: A major constraint in writi=
ng on certain topics related to sadhana (esp mantras) is how much and what =
to put in writing in a public forum. There are bound to be various perspect=
ives and this may distract or confuse the initial practitioner. Moreover th=
e tyranny of over-intellectualization has to be kept in mind. To any such r=
eader my advice is- please follow what you are doing currently. Things will=
 evolve and happen on their own accord. Whatever is suited to you will happ=
en in the natural flow of Life. <BR><BR>In this post I will also touch upon=
 certain other topics raised in some related posts while primarily addressi=
ng Rajarshi ji's queries.<BR><BR>>>>I had talked to a few people w=
ho adhere to different paramparas >>>within the broader subset of =
